{"tid":1237684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長輩圖是戰勝關鍵 [不斷更新]","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T03:23:18.000Z","uid":263398,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"29fc2aef460be9e3b971cbe3e2d101b1021b0f51","tid":1237684,"uid":263398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"見之前嘅長輩圖好似真係對我地上一輩有作用，所以特登開咗個account，希望出出一份綿力，改變下佢哋嘅諗法！<br />\n<br />\n雖然琴晚200萬人出黎行大家真係好叻，但我地要知，其實仲有500萬人未表態(除左簽左名果90萬但最後得20個出黎行嘅同胞啦)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正正因為咁，係林太眼中7個先得2個人出黎行，所以咪覺得係<strong>少數意見</strong>，不撤回囉！<br />\n<br />\n所以我地除咗要keep 住200萬，都要不繼壯大，令林太知道大部分香港人嘅聲音！<br />\n<br />\n本人覺得上一輩都唔係傻嘅，太假嘅句子好難改變到佢哋諗法。所以我創作靈感都係 based on 事實再exlaborate～<br />\n<br />\n以下係今日見到嘅 news 所整嘅2張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/17/232105_2c5f739f70d8d157723ac90128231e97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2F232105_2c5f739f70d8d157723ac90128231e97.jpg&h=78d2939d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依張好明顯係想話俾上一輩知：下屆投票知邊個應該投，邊個唔應該投<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/17/232120_ee26ceb6ff5d7ecd842662d2fb17b356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2F232120_ee26ceb6ff5d7ecd842662d2fb17b356.jpg&h=c15e4009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依張就同支持警察嘅人講：你繼續支持警察依法執法啦，下個拉你/你屋企人唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家<strong>多多 share俾自己上一輩</strong>，等佢哋知香港處於水深火熱之中啦！<br />\n<strong>#會不斷更新 同 改善<br />\n#有任何idea/ 可以令張圖表達更好都可以提出</strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，希望唔好變返5年前黃藍絲，香港人打香港人！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港加油！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04e8565cf7c1e9940680aa5e1e006c8f19a5032","tid":1237684,"uid":172385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29fc2aef460be9e3b971cbe3e2d101b1021b0f51","tid":1237684,"uid":263398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"見之前嘅長輩圖好似真係對我地上一輩有作用，所以特登開咗個account，希望出出一份綿力，改變下佢哋嘅諗法！<br />\n<br />\n雖然琴晚200萬人出黎行大家真係好叻，但我地要知，其實仲有500萬人未表態(除左簽左名果90萬但最後得20個出黎行嘅同胞啦)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正正因為咁，係林太眼中7個先得2個人出黎行，所以咪覺得係<strong>少數意見</strong>，不撤回囉！<br />\n<br />\n所以我地除咗要keep 住200萬，都要不繼壯大，令林太知道大部分香港人嘅聲音！<br />\n<br />\n本人覺得上一輩都唔係傻嘅，太假嘅句子好難改變到佢哋諗法。所以我創作靈感都係 based on 事實再exlaborate～<br />\n<br />\n以下係今日見到嘅 news 所整嘅2張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/17/232105_2c5f739f70d8d157723ac90128231e97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2F232105_2c5f739f70d8d157723ac90128231e97.jpg&h=78d2939d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依張好明顯係想話俾上一輩知：下屆投票知邊個應該投，邊個唔應該投<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/17/232120_ee26ceb6ff5d7ecd842662d2fb17b356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2F232120_ee26ceb6ff5d7ecd842662d2fb17b356.jpg&h=c15e4009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依張就同支持警察嘅人講：你繼續支持警察依法執法啦，下個拉你/你屋企人唔好喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家<strong>多多 share俾自己上一輩</strong>，等佢哋知香港處於水深火熱之中啦！<br />\n<strong>#會不斷更新 同 改善<br />\n#有任何idea/ 可以令張圖表達更好都可以提出</strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，希望唔好變返5年前黃藍絲，香港人打香港人！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港加油！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\